00:02.176 --> 00:03.090
[laughing]

00:03.177 --> 00:04.656
Look out for the tickle monster!

00:04.743 --> 00:06.528
He's going to get you.
[car alarm chirps]

00:08.878 --> 00:10.662
[alarm chirps]

00:12.882 --> 00:14.449
[alarm chirps]

00:16.233 --> 00:18.018
[alarm chirps]

00:18.670 --> 00:20.846
[alarm chirps]

00:22.283 --> 00:24.589
Honey, you can stop
looking for the car keys.

00:26.113 --> 00:29.159
♪ Yes, no, maybe ♪

00:29.246 --> 00:32.031
♪ I don't know ♪

00:32.119 --> 00:35.383
